body.value:
Ask a Tutoring Question : This form is for tutoring related questions going to lib-tutoring@fsu.edu

Bradley Reading Room : Faculty and graduate student request for access to the reading room in Scholars Commons

Book Search : Ask us to search for a book you can't find

Claim Returned : Returned an item but still see it listed on your account?

Consultation Request : Scheduled One-on-one help with a librarian subject specialist.

Course Reserve Item Request : Faculty and TA's may request items be placed on reserve for a course

Faculty Extended Time Individual Study Room Request : Form for requesting a study room for a semester

Giving materials to the libraries : When you give items to the libraries, like books, DVD's, etc. this form is a request for a tax document.

Graduate Student Extended Time Individual Study Room Request : Form for requesting a study room for two weeks

Instruction Request : A form for instructors wishing to arrange instruction for courses

Interlibrary Loan Account Assistance : Are you having trouble logging into to your ILL account?

Library Express Delivery service (LEDs) is for Faculty and Teaching Assistants to ask for materials to be delivered to their departments.

  • LED Library Express Delivery Materials Pickup Request
  • LED Library Express Delivery Registration
  • Panama City, FL Campus Library Express Delivery Service Request
  • Westminster Oaks Delivery

Materials Purchase Suggestions : Faculty may suggest items to purchase using this form -- requires log-in

Need data about the library? : The Libraries Assessment Department can help you find the data you need for your research about the Florida State University Libraries.

Off-Campus Access Solutions : Can't connect from off-campus? Start here.

Open Access Fund Proposal : Funding consideration for Open Access Publishing.

Pay for Lost Materials : Use this form to report that you lost an item.

Website Problem or Suggestion : Notice a mistake, or something wrong? We would really like to know

Special Collection Forms

Special Collections & Archives Reading Room Access Form : Registration form to use the Special Collections and Archives Reading Room.

Special Collections & Archives Class Visit Request Form : If you want to bring your class or community group to Special Collections & Archives for an instructional visit, use this form to schedule it

Special Collections & Archives Reproduction Request Form : If you need a digital image of materials in Special Collections & Archives, use this form to request it
